{
  "texts": [
    "Emergent language has made a step towards human-like language.",
    "However, whether machines communicate in a human-like way and can learn a human-interpretable language is still unclear.",
    "A great number of existing works regarding learning tasks with communication seek hidden, deep, and obscure codes for messages [47,48,78,91], which still need to be further interpreted and understood.",
    "ConclusionsOur survey proposes to classify the literature based on 9 dimensions.",
    "These dimensions constitute the basis of designing Comm-MADRL systems."
  ]
}